- ğŸ”” **Real-time Notifications:** Instant notifications for appointment confirmations, reminders, and updates.
- ğŸ’³ **Integrated Payment Options:** Secure payment gateway integration for hassle-free transactions.
- â­ **Ratings & Reviews:** Users can rate and review their experiences to help others choose the best services.
- ğŸ“± **Responsive Design:** Optimized for both mobile and tablet devices to ensure a smooth user experience.

